# ==============================================================================
# GITIGNORE FOR HIGH-FIDELITY BIONIC ARM PROJECT
# ==============================================================================

# 1. Ignore everything by default
*

# 2. Allow Git to look inside directory structures (CRITICAL for subfolders)
!*/

# 3. Whitelist all Jupyter Notebook files across the repo
!*.ipynb

# 4. Whitelist the entire Firmware folder and all its contents
!Firmware/**

# 5. Whitelist all image assets (.jpg, .jpeg, .png)
!*.jpg
!*.jpeg
!*.png

# 6. Whitelist other documentation files
!README.md
!survey_responses.xlsx

# 7. Track the .gitignore file itself
!.gitignore